These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-1::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  lawyer, manager, nurse, paramedic, pilot, security-guard
6 different games are played: scrabble, canasta, domino, billiard, monopoly, mah-jongg
 1. the person playing domino is on the left of the lawyer##1
 2. the manager is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
 3. the manager is somewhere to the right of the person playing scrabble##5
 4. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the left of the nurse##8
 5. the security-guard is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
 6. the person playing monopoly is somewhere between the person playing domino and the security-guard##7
 7. the lawyer is not to the left of the person playing domino##8
 8. the pilot is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
 9. the security-guard is on the left or right of the pilot##3
10. the person playing scrabble is not to the left of the paramedic##8
11. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the right of the paramedic##5
12. the manager is on the right of the paramedic##1
13. the nurse is somewhere to the right of the person playing domino##5
14. the security-guard is somewhere between the person playing canasta and the nurse##7
15. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the right of the person playing scrabble##5
16. the pilot is not the person playing billiard##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |   4   |       5        |   6   |
| Job           | paramedic | manager | lawyer | pilot | security-guard | nurse |
| Game   | scrabble | domino    | canasta  | monopoly  | billiard            | mah-jongg  |

