.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-3::.
City: boston, berlin, miami, rome, liverpool, paris
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: basketball, biathlon, cricket, sailing, soccer, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to miami##5
 2. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##5
 3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to liverpool##5
 4. the person who's sport is cricket is not to the left of the person traveling to berlin##8
 5. the person traveling to miami is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
 6. the person traveling to paris is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami##3
 7. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to miami##5
 8. the person traveling to rome is not to the right of the person traveling to rome##8
 9. the person traveling to boston is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to miami##5
10. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far right##1
11. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere between the person traveling to liverpool and the person who's sport is cricket##7
12. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
13. the person traveling to paris is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
14. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
15. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person traveling to boston##7
16. the person who's sport is soccer is not to the left of the person who's sport is soccer##8
17. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##5
18. the person traveling to liverpool is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
19. the person who's sport is cricket is not the person traveling to boston##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |       4       |     5     |    6     |
| City   | liverpool   | miami | paris    | rome      | berlin | boston |
| Sport         | biathlon | soccer  | basketball | weightlifting | cricket   | sailing  |

