.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |     4      |     5     |    6     |
| Job   | dressmaker | architect | accountant  | pilot     | lawyer | entrepreneur |
| Pet           | cat        | goat    | turtle | chinchilla | horse     | hamster  |

