 3. the person driving the motorbike is not the person drinking milk##6
 4. the person drinking 7up is not to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##8
 5. the person drinking lemonade is in an even position##4
 6. the person drinking 7up is not to the left of the person driving the scooter##8
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
 8. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person driving the helicopter##5
 9. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
10. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
11. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
