The people prefer 6 different music-genres: classical, jazz, reggae, rock, salsa, techno
 1. the person eating corn is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 2. the person eating corn is not to the right of the fan of rock##8
 3. the fan of classical is somewhere to the right of the fan of reggae##5
 4. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the left of the person eating blueberry##5
 5. the fan of rock is not to the left of the person eating corn##8
 6. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
 7. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the right of the fan of classical##5
 8. the fan of salsa is not the person eating grapes##6
 9. the person eating blueberry is on the left or right of the person eating grapes##3
