13. the fan of classical is somewhere to the right of the person eating peach##5
14. the fan of rock is in an odd position##4
15. the fan of techno is somewhere to the right of the fan of classical##5
16. the fan of techno is the person eating spinach##1
17. the person eating blueberry is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapes##5
18. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the left of the person eating blueberry##5
19. the person eating blueberry is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
